        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"286\">@Mengyang Zhou</span>, <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"213\">@SBachman</span>,  does OceanParcels support computing back-trajectories? The forward problem is interesting, because we can tag a parcel of water and see where it goes. Back trajectories are interesting because, for example, if we have an observation at a point, we can see where the water came from.</p>",
