        "content": "<p>This paper is focused on atmospheric dynamics, but seems relevant to the questions at hand:<br>\n<a href=\"https://journals.ametsoc.org/view/journals/atsc/51/4/1520-0469_1994_051_0530_cawsat_2_0_co_2.xml?tab_body=pdf\">https://journals.ametsoc.org/view/journals/atsc/51/4/1520-0469_1994_051_0530_cawsat_2_0_co_2.xml?tab_body=pdf</a></p>",
        "id": 56154,
